OL,6,FThe festivities are over but in the
OL,7,Fcold light of January, it's the real
OL,8,Fcost of Christmas that is at the
OL,9,Fforefront of people's minds. In fact,
OL,10,Ffor those already facing financial
OL,11,Fhardship it is often all they can
OL,12,Fthink about and knowing where to turn
OL,13,Ffor help and support can be daunting.
OL,15,FFor one young mum from south Wales,
OL,16,Fwho spoke to ITV News anonymously, she
OL,17,Fknows firsthand how hard it can be.
