OL,3,CLoan shark victim who 'lived in fear'
OL,4,Cwarns others of illegal lenders
OL,6,FA few years ago she was in need of
OL,7,Fsome basic essentials for her children
OL,8,Fbut living 'pay cheque to pay cheque'
OL,9,Fand having a poor credit rating meant
OL,10,Fshe wasn't able to borrow from a bank.
OL,11,FSo she turned to a local illegal money
OL,12,Flender also known as a loan shark.
OL,14,FThe use of Loan Sharks is happening up
OL,15,Fand down the country, particularly in
OL,16,Fsmall, local communities, and is a
OL,17,Fhuge underreported problem.
