OL,4,Cwarns others of illegal lenders
OL,6,FIt is breaking the law for anyone who
OL,7,Fis not authorised by the Financial
OL,8,FConduct Authority (FCA) to lend money
OL,9,Fbut according to the latest figures by
OL,10,FStop Loan Sharks Wales, an
OL,11,Forganisation that investigates and
OL,12,Fprosecutes Loan Sharks throughout
OL,13,FWales, sixty per cent of those that
OL,14,Fnow come forward have used an illegal
OL,15,Fmoney lender or Loan Shark to cover
OL,16,Feveryday expenses.
