OL,6,FA few years ago, people would only
OL,7,Ftend to use them in order to purchase
OL,8,Funexpectedly needed or significant
OL,9,Fitems such as a new fridge, freezer or
OL,10,Fcar.
OL,12,FThere has also been a significant
OL,13,Fchange in the victim demographics in
OL,14,Frecent years. Now, more than 80 per
OL,15,Fcent of victims are in employment,
OL,16,Falbeit mostly part-time or on zero-
OL,17,Fhour contracts, compared to just 40
OL,18,Fper cent pre-2022.
