OL,6,FFor some people, it isn't always
OL,7,Fobvious that lending money in this way
OL,8,Fis illegal or that they are victims of
OL,9,FLoan Sharks.
OL,11,FThe woman we spoke to said she hadn't
OL,12,Frealised that the man she was
OL,13,Fborrowing money from was a 'Loan
OL,14,FShark' and that what he was doing was
OL,15,Fa crime. She described how, in the
OL,16,Fearly days, he seemed "kind" and
OL,17,F"friendly" and "gained her trust".
OL,19,F"(He was) lovely, when I first
OL,20,Fstarted. I actually thought they were
OL,21,Fa friend," she explained.
