OL,6,F"When I started saying I couldn't pay
OL,7,Fthe amount I was paying, that was when
OL,8,Fthings started to get a bit messy if
OL,9,Fyou want to say....the threats then
OL,10,Flike the car, bailiffs things like
OL,11,Fthat."
OL,13,FShe initially began by borrowing
OL,14,Faround a thousand pounds.
