OL,6,FUnbeknown to her, the interest he was
OL,7,Fcharging ranged from thirty percent to
OL,8,Fa thousand percent. Soon the loan
OL,9,Fshark began taking every penny she
OL,10,Fhad, including her child maintenance
OL,11,Fpayment. She said she was caught in a
OL,12,F"spiral" of having to borrow more
OL,13,Fmoney from him to repay him what she
OL,14,Fowed.
