OL,3,CLoan shark victim who 'lived in fear'
OL,4,Cwarns others of illegal lenders
OL,6,FShe said: "I'd tell him I don't have
OL,7,Fit and he wouldn't believe me so I'd
OL,8,Fsend him screenshots of my bank but
OL,9,Fsay there was #20 or #30 left in there
OL,10,Fhe'd still want that so he'd take my
OL,11,Flast. I'd have to pay him whatever I
OL,12,Fhad.
OL,14,F"I'd literally have nothing and then
OL,15,Fwould have to go and borrow off
OL,16,Ffriends and family then for essentials
OL,17,Flike bread, milk, nappies."
