OL,3,CLoan shark victim who 'lived in fear'
OL,4,Cwarns others of illegal lenders
OL,6,F"I stopped going out with my friends.
OL,7,FI literally stopped everything and it
OL,8,Fwas just the anxiety that would sit
OL,9,Fwith me like constantly I wouldn't
OL,10,Fsleep very well in the nights,
OL,11,Fnothing. It was just constant dread."
OL,13,FThis went on for several years until
OL,14,Fshe finally found the courage to
OL,15,Freport what was happening. She said it
OL,16,Fwas a mix of emotions that kept her
OL,17,Ffrom doing so sooner. She described
OL,18,Ffeeling "stupid" and "embarrassed".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/12
