OL,4,Cwarns others of illegal lenders
OL,6,FShe also said that despite everything
OL,7,Fthe loan shark had put her through she
OL,8,Ffelt she was "betraying him".
OL,10,FHowever, after picking up the phone to
OL,11,FStop Loan Shark Wales she said she has
OL,12,Fnot looked back. She has had support
OL,13,Fwith all of her financial needs as
OL,14,Fwell as housing. She said she feels
OL,15,Fcomplete "relief" at having broken the
OL,16,Ffinancial cycle she found herself in.
OL,18,FSo what is a loan shark?
